data.description: Spectacular living near the Texas Gulf Coast on your own 3 acre mini ranch. An ease to get to your favorite fishing spot, marina or work. This house has a total make over on the inside. Upgrades galore. Here are some to mention: New kitchen cabinets & drawers all with soft close, granite countertops, new appliances that includes double ovens, dishwasher, garbage disposal, full size refrigerator & freezer. New ceiling fans, all new bathrooms & fixtures, hot water heater, paint, lights, all new pex plumbing & tile flooring with vapor barrier throughout.  As soon as you walk in the door you will fall in love with the kitchen with enough room for the whole family to enjoy. Split floor plan &  an office that could double as a 4th bedroom.  Separate breakfast & dining area. Inside utility. Backyard has a stunning oak tree with plenty of space for all your outdoor activities. Barn with stalls and pasture is fenced. Mom-in-law quarters that could be finished out. Has RV 50 amp & water hook-up
